name: ImmutableStackTest
description: Unit tests for the ImmutableStack class, focusing on its behavior with various operations like push, pop, peek, and iterator.

test_cases.name: testNewStackIsEmpty
test_cases.description: Tests that a newly created stack is empty.

test_cases.name: testPopOnEmptyStackThrowsException
test_cases.description: Tests that popping from an empty stack throws a RuntimeException.

test_cases.name: testPeekOnEmptyStackThrowsException
test_cases.description: Tests that peeking from an empty stack throws a RuntimeException.

test_cases.name: testRemoveThrowsException
test_cases.description: Tests that calling remove on the iterator of a stack throws a RuntimeException.

test_cases.name: testStackIsEmptyAfterPushThenPop
test_cases.description: Tests that a stack is empty after pushing an item and then popping it.

test_cases.name: testPeekGivesLastPushed
test_cases.description: Tests that peeking returns the last pushed item.

test_cases.name: testPopPeekGivesSecondLastPushed
test_cases.description: Tests that after popping, peeking returns the second last pushed item.

test_cases.name: testIteratorWhenEmpty
test_cases.description: Tests that the iterator of an empty stack has no next item.

test_cases.name: testIteratorWhenHasOneItem
test_cases.description: Tests that the iterator of a stack with one item has a next item.

test_cases.name: testIteratorReturnsOneItem
test_cases.description: Tests that the iterator returns the pushed item.

test_cases.name: testIteratorReturnsLastPushedFirst
test_cases.description: Tests that the iterator returns the last pushed item first.

test_cases.name: testIteratorReturnsTwoItemsInOrderOfPop
test_cases.description: Tests that the iterator returns two items in the order they would be popped.
